ome,Safari 浏览器 15 个以内标签页还有一堆插件\r\n* Alfred2,Magnet,iStatistica\r\n* 微信\r\n\r\n\r\n![img]( https://i.imgur.com/HWhE70W.png)\r\n\r\n仅供参考，勿喷", "content_rendered": "<p>网上一大堆顶配测试，其实我只关心丐版能力</p>\n<p>实在等不了定制版的时间，看到苹果店现场有货就提了一台 Macbook Pro 16 寸丐版 16G 内存</p>\n<ul>\n<li>外接了一台 3440*1440 的带鱼显示器</li>\n<li>PD Win11 虚拟机，内存给了 2G</li>\n<li>DockerDesktop ，裸跑 2.5G 内存</li>\n<li>Lightroom 打开了一张 A7R4 的 Raw 图片</li>\n<li>VSCode 跑起来一个 AntDesignPro 项目</li>\n<li>Firefox,Chrome,Safari 浏览器 15 个以内标签页还有一堆插件</li>\n<li>Alfred2,Magnet,iStatistica</li>\n<li>微信</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img alt=\"img\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HWhE70W.png\"/></p>\n<p>仅供参考，勿喷</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635475968, "replies": 42, "id": 811461}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_large.png?m=1630576655", "name": "hardware", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_normal.png?m=1630576655", "title": "硬件", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware", "topics": 4082, "footer": "", "header": "硬件发烧友的讨论节点", "title_alternative": "Hardware", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655", "stars": 1865, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 52, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"username": "z0ro", "website": "blog.codingli.cn", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fdc567d1fefa00d5e62c78df53226618?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/z0ro", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1568341643, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fdc567d1fefa00d5e62c78df53226618?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fdc567d1fefa00d5e62c78df53226618?s=24&d=retro", "location": "beijing", "btc": "", "id": 441080}, "last_reply_by": "zxCoder", "last_touched": 1635527304, "title": "有鉴别矿卡的路子吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/811557", "created": 1635495382, "deleted": 0, "content": "双十一想组台主机，但是怕